    <rjw_genes_animal_inheritance_settings_added_as_xenogene_key>基因作为异种基因</rjw_genes_animal_inheritance_settings_added_as_xenogene_key>
    <rjw_genes_animal_inheritance_settings_added_as_xenogene_explanation>如果启用，动物基因将被添加为异种基因。</rjw_genes_animal_inheritance_settings_added_as_xenogene_explanation>

